title: Nero 2014 Platinum Patch Files + Keygen Crack (Any current versi
description:
This is a crack that I found at, so thanks to all of them.
How works the Crack?:

1)Install Nero latest version with trial mode.
2)After installation ,CLOSE ALL the NERO apps.
3)Download the Activator. Run Activator.Then click Patch button (wait few minutes,a windows should appear saying Patching in Progress..)
4)After Patching completes,Click Generate button and copy a Serial Number, not the Patent Activation Code.
5)Now open Nero Control Center.
6)Right click on each key and Remove all of them.
7)Click Add button and paste the serial key you copied from Crack.
8)Click Next ! Activated.
